1. `api_refresh_usage_diff_current_frontend`
2. `api_align_media_sign_route`
3. `api_fix_checkout_session`
4. `api_fix_media_presign`
5. `api_fix_media_complete`
6. `api_fix_payments_plans`
7. `api_fix_payments_subscription`
8. `api_fix_payments_orders`
9. `api_fix_payments_create_subscription`
10. `api_fix_payments_stripe_create_session`
11. `media_align_lesson_upload_surfaces`
